            </description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">于和伟</dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 22 May 2021 18:30:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://www.zhihu.com/question/451738975/answer/1863134062</guid></item><item><title>条漫和页漫的区别是什么？</title><link>http://www.zhihu.com/question/68118338/answer/1895509895?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8b388ced5c1c4129fc0f6656f6953933_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="514" data-rawheight="4096" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-8b388ced5c1c4129fc0f6656f6953933" data-watermark-src="v2-68d7cd553504951b03c46ff4158f91bf" data-private-watermark-src="v2-62197aad09ffb37431a0a5ec9a184d79" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b24b3ce8e19660c70e1f5df1e60832c3_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-b24b3ce8e19660c70e1f5df1e60832c3" data-watermark-src="v2-9cf048c0da2823aca1984c73ab5c2a3d" data-private-watermark-src="v2-dd484d6ebf39827ef5a4ebe8b69c4968" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-32a57b0a61291d378139248ba591955e_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-32a57b0a61291d378139248ba591955e" data-watermark-src="v2-3345ade355e1aa84b0d5e04a6e622767" data-private-watermark-src="v2-c9170a5dfdb99cab877287c19306f0be" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f82dbd304cdc51f3f81f1c56db4163dc_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-f82dbd304cdc51f3f81f1c56db4163dc" data-watermark-src="v2-4841393499d4947a0c9f6afe3147fac6" data-private-watermark-src="v2-d8f9156c1fab9184a29335fb08a1d5ef" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c1e31604c9760ffaa7971ceb5f4f4974_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-c1e31604c9760ffaa7971ceb5f4f4974" data-watermark-src="v2-c1e3f8ce771b94e151f1dfc1862a2d03" data-private-watermark-src="v2-517d043fc0bf2a6f5c1c177952c42e17" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-54c253538be4bc75e223f7094efa3451_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-54c253538be4bc75e223f7094efa3451" data-watermark-src="v2-76498c449f617dc849c16105bd06ca84" data-private-watermark-src="v2-999148203db20cdc8f5c1339e227d3ee" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bd6ad1bd9337115511b9b9aab8c7fd79_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="1227" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-bd6ad1bd9337115511b9b9aab8c7fd79" data-watermark-src="v2-7d0a3d66aa7614c42c812083973edbf8" data-private-watermark-src="v2-6290f3758b33ffd3e71835499216795c" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d0527fd90030ef492a5ee490ab956f92_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-d0527fd90030ef492a5ee490ab956f92" data-watermark-src="v2-ce45908886fc1018d818fd084c190bf2" data-private-watermark-src="v2-a84931bfcd2af34c45be931bd9a31c5b" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-59efb0b0fbeb1d33167e02a49fa5a702_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-59efb0b0fbeb1d33167e02a49fa5a702" data-watermark-src="v2-740ccfdcc2eeb9d0a01ece9a6f54dda6" data-private-watermark-src="v2-adcb76cfa3fca0b52a4220a15fb9fcd3" data-tags="politic" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d3a91b3100210e9ef9ea0f18f618b4e3_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="878" data-rawheight="4096" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-d3a91b3100210e9ef9ea0f18f618b4e3" data-watermark-src="v2-b61bc58add524ec1f6ad44f5f4150811" data-private-watermark-src="v2-6938b9ebda6bdfe50e560befb802d984" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cbcb39e160e1bbe93b9fc886599cb563_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-cbcb39e160e1bbe93b9fc886599cb563" data-watermark-src="v2-d370a0df0d217dc15ad84fe88ffc0d39" data-private-watermark-src="v2-397800be5c654d119b17f8264e49c0d5" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-812740ef6b02f4c0b99a096244a485d4_720w.jpeg?rss" data-rawwidth="1080" data-rawheight="2160" data-size="normal" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-812740ef6b02f4c0b99a096244a485d4" data-watermark-src="v2-8029332042a64f745baed7a8eedbdfc3" data-private-watermark-src="v2-e986a50fef22cd9f8a99f5deca7c7556" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
